    "Fee rates fluctuate based on network congestion. When many people are transacting, competition for block space increases and fees rise. During quieter periods, fees drop." : {
      "comment" : "SendBitcoinView — 'Why do fees change?' explanation",
      "extractionState" : "stale",
      "localizations" : {
        "pt-BR" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "As taxas flutuam com base no congestionamento da rede. Quando muitas pessoas estão transacionando, a concorrência por espaço no bloco aumenta e as taxas sobem. Em períodos mais calmos, as taxas caem."
          }
        }
      }
    },
